My four forks are for the recipe below, from Tony of Fresno also. I had been waiting for years to make a Lemon Pudding Cake recipe I clipped from Gourmet. Instead, I made Tony's below, which was very similar. Couple of changes: I used 1/2 cup of flour vs. 1/4 and it was fabulous. I also did not use cream of tartar. I substituted regular lemons for Meyer lemons. House guests RAVED about this dish.

