This was absolutely delicious! After reading the other reviews and looking at several recipes, I realized the 1 cup of lemon juice was probably intended to be 1 juiced lemon, about 1/4 to 1/3 cup. I kept almost everything else the same, and it worked out great; I substituted strawberries for raspberries and my friend and husband loved it. It's very good and light-tasting, and also very fast to make.

