Rating: 1
Much to my surprise (and horror), this is the absolute worst recipe I've ever seen on Epicurious. Be VERY wary of this recipe, as it will NOT work. The mixture is much too liquidy, and lining your baking pan with plastic wrap will make nothing but a melted plastic mess. I've tried other lemon pudding cakes with great success, but this is definitely not one to attempt.